Package com.safenetinc.luna.provider.keygen

Contains classes that implement key generators to create new Luna secret keys and public/private key pairs.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
LunaKeyGeneratorAes A key-generator engine for AES keys.
LunaKeyGeneratorAria A key-generator engine for ARIA keys.
LunaKeyGeneratorDes A key-generator engine for DES keys.
LunaKeyGeneratorDes2 A key-generator engine for DES2 keys.
LunaKeyGeneratorDes3 A key-generator engine for DES3 keys.
LunaKeyGeneratorGenericSecret A key-generator engine for generic secret keys.
LunaKeyGeneratorRc2 A key-generator engine for RC2 keys.
LunaKeyGeneratorRc4 A key-generator engine for RC4 keys.
LunaKeyGeneratorRc5 A key-generator engine for RC5 keys.
LunaKeyGeneratorSecret Base class for all key generator engine classes.
LunaKeyPairGeneratorDh Engine class for generating Diffie-Hellman key pairs.
LunaKeyPairGeneratorDsa Engine class for generating DSA key pairs.
LunaKeyPairGeneratorEc Engine class for generating EC DSA key pairs.
LunaKeyPairGeneratorEcWithExtraRandomBits Engine class for generating EC DSA key pairs with Extra Random Bits (for GBCS).
LunaKeyPairGeneratorRsa Engine class for generating RSA key pairs.
LunaKeyPairGeneratorRsaX931 Engine class for generating RSA X9.31 key pairs.
 

Package com.safenetinc.luna.provider.keygen Description

Contains classes that implement key generators to create new Luna secret keys and public/private key pairs.
